## plugin catalog

| Plugin | Platform | ID | Version | Summary | Docs |
|--------|----------|-----|--------|---------|------|
| [AI Chat File Links](jetbrains/ai-chat-file-links/) | JetBrains (PyCharm, IDEA, …) | `com.aichat.filelinks` | 0.2.0 | Opens files from **AI Chat** when URL / “file does not exist” errors occur; **Dismiss error notification when the file opens successfully** (Settings → Tools → AI Chat File Links) closes the error balloon after open | [readme.md](jetbrains/ai-chat-file-links/readme.md) · [readme_ru.md](jetbrains/ai-chat-file-links/readme_ru.md) |

